  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed front roof lights, by reason of their positioning, would adversely affect the character of a locally listed building as well as the character of the Ealing Town Centre Conservation Area and the visual amenity of the streetscene and is against the Article 4 Direction for Ealing Town Centre - The Grove. As such the proposal would be contrary to section 16 of the National Planning Policy Framework (2019), policies D3, D4, D6 and HC1 of the London Plan (2021), Policy 1.1 of Development Strategy 2026 (2012); policies 7.4, 7B and 7C of the Development Management Development Plan Document (2013); and the Ealing Town Centre Conservation Area Management Plan. The applicant please refer to Officer's Report for detailed reasoning."
